1.0.name: wordpress/bizway
1.0.description: BizWay is a Professional and beautiful Responsive WordPress Theme built by InkThemes.com. BizWay is one of the easiest themes to build your Web Presence in 10 Minutes or less, in few Simple Steps. The Theme with the presence of Theme Options Panel, makes it easy for you to have your own branded new Website for your Business or Personal Use in Minutes. The Theme features a uniquely designed Home Page and a blog page template and is widgetized. I am pretty sure, You will absolutely love using the BizWay Theme.
